Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.23,Title,,0,0,0,,{\p1\an7\frz0\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(0,0)\clip(396.02,476.87,452.41,541.84)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 1080 0 1080
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.63,0:01:09.34,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}命运正召唤着我们登上这盛大舞台
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.63,0:01:15.89,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}胸膛里聚光灯闪耀  脑海中思绪沸腾
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.35,0:01:23.61,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\t(5010,5010,\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&)}追梦路上  我们前赴后继洒下热泪
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.61,0:01:28.69,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使唱到心碎  仍愿相信
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.99,0:01:31.61,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}曙光就等在前方
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.61,0:01:35.07,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}你和我  共携手
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.07,0:01:38.37,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}奔赴到路尽头
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.70,0:01:42.37,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}夜空下我们也可向星辰许愿
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.37,0:01:46.13,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}向着光来的方向
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.30,0:01:50.97,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}勇敢伸出手吧  抓住那伟大的愿望
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.97,0:01:54.64,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不用管它是否是别人眼中的白日梦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.64,0:01:58.81,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}就算「最闪耀的星星将最早迎来熄灭」
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.81,0:02:02.14,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}我们也会打破这命运
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.40,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}面对无人可知的明天
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.40,0:02:09.28,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}只需听从内心的声音
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.28,0:02:12.90,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}去奔跑  去超越
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.74,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}将梦与未来
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.74,0:02:19.16,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}交织在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.75,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}用我最珍贵的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:09.34,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}hey, 運命が呼んでいる{\fscx50} {\fscx100}for the big stage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:15.89,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}the spotlight filling my heart{\fscx50} {\fscx100}また熱くなる想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:23.61,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\t(5010,5010,\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&)}Ah, 夢追って淚した{\fscx50} {\fscx100}ones before me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:28.69,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I sing through the heartbreak{\fscx50} {\fscx100}信じたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:31.61,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}光が待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:35.07,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}I've got you You've got me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:38.37,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}最後まで進んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:42.37,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}Oh in the night we can wish on a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:46.13,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}光の先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:50.97,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}手を伸ばし続けた{\fscx50} {\fscx100}big dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:54.64,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}誰かの目には{\fscx50} {\fscx100}it's a daydream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:58.81,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}“All the stars that shine brightest, Burn out the fastest”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:02.14,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}ぼくら越えていける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.40,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誰も知らない{\fscx50} {\fscx100}tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:09.28,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}心の声だけ{\fscx50} {\fscx100}follow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:12.90,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}駆け抜けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.74,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}夢と未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:19.16,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}重なるように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.75,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}with my pledge
Dialogue: 3,0:22:10.73,0:22:18.40,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}曾经对着镜子拭去眼泪  追逐梦想
Dialogue: 3,0:22:18.53,0:22:21.99,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在那个地方
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.53,0:22:30.71,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}连好好给自己一个拥抱都做不到的懊悔
Dialogue: 3,0:22:30.71,0:22:36.13,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}和自尊一同  在房间中回荡
Dialogue: 3,0:22:36.29,0:22:42.80,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}珍贵的时间渐渐被夺走
Dialogue: 3,0:22:42.80,0:22:49.93,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现今我正走在那条
Dialogue: 3,0:22:49.93,0:22:54.69,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不曾放弃追寻的理想之路上
Dialogue: 3,0:22:54.69,0:22:57.69,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}要以比那时更为充实的自己
Dialogue: 3,0:22:57.69,0:23:03.15,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}去同回忆相会
Dialogue: 3,0:23:04.20,0:23:10.54,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使身处告别之中
Dialogue: 3,0:23:10.54,0:23:17.09,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们也在不断堆砌各自的理想
Dialogue: 3,0:23:17.09,0:23:21.21,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}虽然与梦中盼望的那个日子
Dialogue: 3,0:23:21.21,0:23:28.05,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}仍然相距甚远
Dialogue: 3,0:23:28.05,0:23:31.31,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但我还是想将其留到未来
Dialogue: 3,0:23:31.31,0:23:34.52,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}为了将来的我
Dialogue: 3,0:23:34.52,0:23:38.06,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}能够由衷展露笑颜
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.73,0:22:18.40,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}鏡に向かい涙を拭き夢を追ってた
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.53,0:22:21.99,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}あの場所には
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.53,0:22:30.71,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}自分を抱きしめてあげられない悔しさ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.71,0:22:36.13,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}プライドが部屋を交差してた
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.29,0:22:42.80,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}大事な時間が奪われていく
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.80,0:22:49.93,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}諦めず探した理想の道を今
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.93,0:22:54.69,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}歩いてあの頃以上に
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.69,0:22:57.69,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}満たされた私で
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.69,0:23:03.15,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}思い出に会いにいくよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.20,0:23:10.54,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}さようならの中でも
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.54,0:23:17.09,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}それぞれ理想積み上げてたんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.09,0:23:21.21,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}夢焦がれたあの日には
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.21,0:23:28.05,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}程遠いみたいだけどまだ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.05,0:23:31.31,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}未来にとっておくよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:31.31,0:23:34.52,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}これからの私を
Dialogue: 1,0:23:34.52,0:23:38.06,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}楽しめるように
